---
title: Lemony Almond Crusted Chicken with Kale and Carrot Ribbon Salad
description: Tonight's kale and carrot salad is tossed in an apricot vinaigrette that highlights the natural sweetness of its crunchy almond chicken topper! Packed with flavour and texture, this meal is as beautiful as it is tasty!

